01:40:46,757 --> 01:40:49,101
<font color="#ffff00">Itu milikmu.</font>

1110
01:40:49,844 --> 01:40:51,678
<font color="#ffff00">Jika kau pantas memilikinya.</font>

1111
01:40:51,679 --> 01:40:54,182
<font color="#ffff00">Akan kucoba.</font>

1112
01:40:55,599 --> 01:41:00,321
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah tak bisa merestuimu.
