1113
01:41:01,272 --> 01:41:02,945
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tahu.</font>

1114
01:41:05,776 --> 01:41:09,121
<font color="#ffff00">Meski Ayah bangga
dengan dirimu yang sekarang...,</font>

1115
01:41:09,613 --> 01:41:11,957
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah tetap tak bisa mengatakannya.</font>

1116
01:41:14,451 --> 01:41:18,081
<font color="#ffff00">Itu hanya dapat dikatakan
dari hati Ayah.</font>

1117
01:41:19,456 --> 01:41:20,878
<font color="#ffff00">Pergilah...,</font>

1118
01:41:21,959 --> 01:41:23,461
<font color="#ffff00">Anakku.</font>

1119
01:41:25,588 --> 01:41:26,840
<font color="#ffff00">Terima kasih, Ayah.</font>

1120
01:41:42,438 --> 01:41:43,485
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak.</font>

1121
01:41:44,815 --> 01:41:46,488
<font color="#ffff00">Aku yang berterima kasih.</font>

1122
01:41:46,989 --> 01:42:08,089
<font color="#ffff00">Lebah Ganteng</font>
<font color="#33ffff">http://dunia-lebah.blogspot.com</font>

1123
01:44:04,496 --> 01:44:06,919
<font color="#ffff00">Kuperkenalkan pada kalian...,</font>

1124
01:44:07,624 --> 01:44:11,128
<font color="#ffff00">Taneleer Tivan, sang Kolektor.</font>

1125
01:44:12,629 --> 01:44:13,801
<font color="#ffff00">Whoa...</font>

1126
01:44:16,884 --> 01:44:21,435
<font color="#ffff00">Para ksatria Asgard,
