1127
01:44:25,142 --> 01:44:27,236
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tahu kenapa kami di sini.</font>

1128
01:44:30,939 --> 01:44:32,862
<font color="#ffff00">Tentu.</font>

1129
01:44:33,692 --> 01:44:35,945
<font color="#ffff00">Tapi, kalau aku boleh bertanya...,</font>

1130
01:44:36,111 --> 01:44:39,991
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa tidak disimpan
di ruangan besi kalian ?</font>

1131
01:44:40,115 --> 01:44:43,039
<font color="#ffff00">Sudah ada Tesseract di Asgard.</font>

1132
01:44:43,160 --> 01:44:46,710
<font color="#ffff00">Tak bijak menyimpan dua Infinity Stone
berdekatan [Batu Berkekuatan Hebat].</font>

1133
01:44:47,331 --> 01:44:49,834
<font color="#ffff00">Itu sangat bijak.</font>

1134
01:44:59,676 --> 01:45:01,053
<font color="#ffff00">Aku jamin...,</font>

1135
01:45:02,304 --> 01:45:07,526
<font color="#ffff00">...batunya akan aman di sini...</font>

1136
01:45:09,728 --> 01:45:12,231
<font color="#ffff00">...bersama koleksiku.</font>

1137
01:45:13,398 --> 01:45:15,821
<font color="#ffff00">Pastikanlah.</font>

1138
01:45:34,378 --> 01:45:36,881
<font color="#ffff00">Dapat satu.</font>

1139
01:45:38,382 --> 01:45:40,885
<font color="#ffff00">Lima batu lagi.</font>
